***
Simple extension to allow hide/show of speed slider in NetLogo 

Works in Applet and Application contexts

***
Expansion possibilities -- add other elements of the framing UI that can be hidden/shown.
 
***
Example model can be run in NetLogo 5.0 with extension; 
Example HTML file can be run in browser with double-click.

***
Credits -- Thanks to my daughter, Fiona Brady, who did this as an exercise in recursion.

